<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Bootstrap 5 Website Example</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-dark">
      <div class="container-fluid navbar-expand">
        <ul class="navbar-nav">
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Home</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item dropdown">
            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="navbarDropdownMenuLink" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
              Account
            </a>
            <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="navbarDropdownMenuLink">
              <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Sign In</a></li>
              <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Sign Up</a></li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="display-5">My Portfolio</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Hello, my name is Blake Frazzini. I am a Junior at UCCS and I am studying to obtain my Bachelor's in CS.
      <a href="https://eas.uccs.edu/cs/academics/undergraduate-programs/bachelor-of-science-in-computer-science">
      About the BS in CS @ UCCS</a>.
    </p>

    <p>About me</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
      <div class="border border-bottom-0 rounded-top p-2">
        <li>Proficient in the following Programming Languages</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Javascript</li>
            <li>Java</li>
            <li>C#</li>
            <li>Python</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </div>
      <div class="border p-2">
        <li>Technical Skills</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Version control using git/github</li>
            <li>Collaborative software development</li>
            <li>Object-Oriented Programming</li>
            <li>Good communication skills</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </div>
      <div class="border border-top-0 rounded-bottom p-2">
        <li>Background</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Programmer by hobby</li>
            <li>History in Java development</li>
            <li>History in server administration</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </div>
    </ul>

    <h3>Projects</h3>
    <p style="color: green"><%= notice %></p>

    <div id="projects" class="row g-3 mb-3">
      <% @projects.each do |project| %>
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="p-2 border border-dark border-2 rounded">
            <%= render project %>
            <p>
              <%= link_to "Show this project âžœ", project, class: "btn btn-info btn-sm" %>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <%= link_to "New project", new_project_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
